Wt::Ruby was derived from QtRuby, which in turn was derived from PerlQt.

Wt::Ruby was written by Richard Dale

QtRuby was written by Richard Dale with contributions from:
    Alex Kellet
    Caleb Tennis
    Arno Rehn
    ..and many others (see the ChangeLog for details)

PerlQt3/Smoke was written by:
    Ashley Winters
    Germain Garand
    David Faure

Ashley Winters and David Faure have granted permission for projects derived from
the PerQt code to be licensed under the LGPL

